My wife and kids have been coming here since they opened. It's a perfect place for a quick good breakfast. Walk up and order, no waitress to wait on. It's really the exact same experience as PeiWei. It is a little more difficult to maneuver on busy  days.   Overall it's clean, good and fast. When you have little kids these are the only things you care about!

