pwpl-rxwNRQdgqFz_-qMPg
I love this place. The service is usually fast. The pizza tastes so damn good and the atmosphere is fantastic. The drinks are always good with a full bar and the patio is really nice (never had a belligerent smoker to deal with). The prices aren't going to compete with your local pizza parlor (see Raffael's), but you don't feel bad about paying for your food. Definitely check this place out if you haven't been. You won't regret it.

